1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Scheme.

2
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,240
Empress Dowager.

3
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:07,800
News just came from the Imperial Hospital.

4
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,320
An imperial physician died suddenly.

5
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,450
I have confirmed it.

6
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:11,920
His name

7
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:14,200
is also on the Book of Life and Death.

8
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,120
Empress Dowager.

9
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,840
It seems they come with ill intent this time.

10
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,800
And Liu Chuan needs to deal with the Medicine God Society.

11
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:21,920
Why not let Liu Chuan

12
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,280
lend me a hand?

13
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:24,800
Granted.

14
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,120
Liu Chuan,

15
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,240
I order you to enter the Imperial Hospital.

16
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:31,000
Devise a countermeasure within three days.

17
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:31,800
Do not fail.

18
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,280
Empress Dowager!

19
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,360
Absolutely not!

20
00:01:34,479 --> 00:01:37,800
Liu Chuan is a golden-sword coroner appointed by the Emperor.

21
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:39,800
He shouldn't be the rebel you speak of

22
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,880
who opposes the new policy, right?

23
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,200
Having him in charge,

24
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:45,570
there should be no objections, right?

25
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:46,600
I

26
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,570
have no objections.

27
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,600
Prince Jia, please stay.

28
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,759
I

29
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,690
have other matters to discuss.

30
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,180
I didn't expect you to have such a day.

31
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:07,720
What?

32
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,199
Are you looking down on me?

33
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:11,200
I just didn't expect it to be so fast.

34
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:13,720
Yes.

35
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,280
It feels like a dream.

36
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,600
From the small Yingtian Prefecture

37
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:19,520
to the current Imperial Hospital.

38
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,200
Uncle.

39
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,600
Your methods are too brilliant.

40
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,160
It's just

41
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:27,000
the most basic toxicity test.

42
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,610
You can easily do it too.

43
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:29,960
Not just this.

44
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:30,880
And

45
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:33,480
the way you coaxed the Empress Dowager.

46
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,960
Women,

47
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,930
they just like to be flattered.

48
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,120
Besides,

49
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,160
do you think the Empress Dowager

50
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,690
is really that easy to coax?

51
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:45,079
She was convinced by just a few words from me.

52
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,000
Nephew,

53
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:47,120
besides investigating cases,

54
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,980
you really don't understand worldly wisdom at all.

55
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,600
I am dull.

56
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,400
Behind this matter

57
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,860
lies a struggle over the New Deal.

58
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,440
The first one to oppose it

59
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,770
is the Empress Dowager.

60
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,640
And Prince Jia

61
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,260
is the one working for her.

62
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,040
And those who support the New Deal

63
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:07,100
are naturally on the Emperor's side.

64
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,360
The mother and son

65
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,800
cannot openly fall out with each other.

66
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:12,600
Therefore, the Empress Dowager won't blow this out of proportion.

67
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:14,280
As for a second-rank official,

68
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,740
a slight slip of the tongue

69
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,200
will be seized upon and blown out of proportion.

70
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,520
Instead, a nobody like me

71
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,200
who is involved with neither side

72
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,930
is the most suitable to be used.

73
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,800
Your words are full of wisdom, Uncle.

74
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,930
I have learned a lot.

75
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:29,120
Don't be fooled by the Empress Dowager smiling at me now.

76
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,320
Once the three days are up,

77
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,200
if she doesn't get a satisfactory answer,

78
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,040
all of us

79
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:35,200
will be dragged down as scapegoats.

80
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:36,720
I didn't expect

81
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,800
you to make the court's situation

82
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,920
so clear.

83
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,840
I just studied a little bit of history.

84
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,600
In that case,

85
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,200
you'd better hurry up and find a solution.

86
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:47,040
I think you are even more anxious than the Empress Dowager.

87
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:49,200
But thanks to Prince Jia this time,

88
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,780
you were able to get such strong support.

89
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,240
Tell me,

90
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:56,890
does he want you to be his brother-in-law?

91
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,840
If he had another sister,

92
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,680
I would just endure it.

93
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,540
But that one...

94
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,720
The Princess has arrived.

95
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,120
Here you are.

96
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:05,280
Liuchuan.

97
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:08,800
Why are you here?

98
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:10,800
My brother asked me

99
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,240
to bring these to you.

100
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,040
These are...

101
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:15,960
My brother confiscated these

102
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:18,000
when he wiped out the Medicine God Society.

103
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,930
He said they might be useful to you.

104
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,400
Such great stuff.

105
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,530
Why didn't you bring them out earlier?

106
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,920
My brother said

107
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,440
these were already in the secret archives.

108
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,120
Your status was too low before,

109
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,480
so you couldn't access them.

110
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,400
But now with the Empress Dowager's permission,

111
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,600
there are no longer such restrictions.

112
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:38,740
Thanks.

113
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,680
I'll take your brother out for drinks next time.

114
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,640
And me.

115
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,200
Let's go.

116
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:53,900
No need to examine.

117
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,000
You can tell at a glance.

118
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,600
It's the same cause of death.

119
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,930
Is it really the Medicine God Society?

120
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,160
But where are they now?

121
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,600
Lord Gu.

122
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,920
What's wrong?

123
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,840
Because his name

124
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,320
is also on the Book of Life and Death.

125
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,170
I didn't believe it either.

126
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,000
But now I have to.

127
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,500
Are we really just waiting to die?

128
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:28,520
Useless!

129
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,040
Is this how your master taught you?

130
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,440
Then he's useless too.

131
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,840
My master is not like that.

132
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,170
Then stand up straight.

133
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:40,080
Qiuyue and I

134
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,240
are inconvenienced working in the palace.

135
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,770
We still need to rely on you.

136
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,520
If you lose your fighting spirit,

137
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,050
then we are truly finished.

138
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,600
Yes, Lord Gu.

139
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,600
Right now, besides Liuchuan,

140
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,800
only your skills can rival the Medicine God Society.

141
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,330
He needs your full support.

142
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,800
I understand.

143
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,380
It's just death, isn't it?

144
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,240
Even if I die,

145
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:04,420
I cannot embarrass my master and martial uncle.

146
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,400
That's my nephew.

147
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:11,000
Of course Lord Gu can't be a member of the Medicine God Society.

148
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,800
But

149
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,600
on this Book of Life and Death,

150
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,770
By imperial decree,

151
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:18,200
everyone in the palace whose name is in the Book

152
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,600
will be kept under strict supervision.

153
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,400
No one

154
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,450
is an exception.

155
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,160
Fortunately, you two are not in it,

156
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:23,820
otherwise,

157
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,100
you'd be just like him.

158
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:26,600
Whose decree are you following?

159
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,600
If you lock him up,

160
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,560
who's going to help me solve the case?

161
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,240
You?

162
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:30,840
At this point,

163
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,600
what kind of case is there left to solve?

164
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,400
I advise you to

165
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,240
wake up,

166
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,000
lest

167
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,680
you bring bad luck upon yourselves.

168
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,810
How can a mere mortal

169
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,280
go against the King of Hell?

170
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:41,210
I'm asking you whose order this is.

171
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,380
Of course it's the Emperor

172
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,200
and the Empress Dowager.

173
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:44,800
And

174
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,600
me too.

175
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,530
Brother Liu,

176
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,800
I did this for the stability of the state.

177
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,800
I had no choice but to resort to this.

178
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,920
We must strictly and centrally monitor everyone

179
00:06:57,920 --> 00:07:00,120
according to the Book of Life and Death.

180
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:02,920
Only then can we catch the mastermind behind this.

181
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:10,480
Go.

182
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,010
Brother Liu,

183
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:13,920
just in case,

184
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,360
I have brought my trusted followers

185
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,760
from outside the palace.

186
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:19,400
Each of them is no less skilled than the imperial guards.

187
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,840
If I am not mistaken,

188
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,720
you locking them all up

189
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,330
is not just to catch the mastermind, is it?

190
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,800
Please stay, Prince Jia.

191
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,440
I have something else to discuss with you.

192
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:37,120
The Emperor is obsessed with the new policies

193
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:39,680
and turns a deaf ear to everything else.

194
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,400
The court

195
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:43,240
is also full of flatterers.

196
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:44,960
Right now,

197
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:47,240
only you and I are of one mind.

198
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,159
I

199
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,320
will grant you

200
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,300
the authority to act on my behalf.

201
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,040
But as a last resort,

202
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,800
we will have to sacrifice everyone in the palace

203
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,600
who is on the Life and Death Book.

204
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,280
Use their lives

205
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,580
in exchange for the stability of Ziwei Star.

206
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,640
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

207
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,800
Isn't that just leaving them to die?

208
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,930
According to the Empress Dowager,

209
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,880
sacrificing a few people

210
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:14,130
is better than them causing chaos.

211
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,240
What they are doing

212
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,840
probably won't help anyway.

213
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,480
Since Liu Chuan has entered the palace and joined the game,

214
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:47,480
he can only be deeply involved in it.

215
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,080
In this way,

216
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,010
that matter can proceed smoothly.

217
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,600
It's only a matter of time

218
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,170
before I fulfill my long-cherished wish.

219
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,720
Reporting to the Empress Dowager.

220
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,360
I have already put everyone on the Life and Death Book

221
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,960
under strict surveillance.

222
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:08,530
But there are still some eunuchs who died unnatural deaths.

223
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,000
Thank you for your hard work, Prince Jia.

224
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:14,730
You indeed haven't disappointed my trust in you.

225
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:17,320
I can finally get a good night's sleep.

226
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,600
You can sleep, Your Highness,

227
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:21,040
but what about those who are locked up waiting to die?

228
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,640
That's their fate.

229
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:23,660
So many people,

230
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,260
how can you just leave them to their doom?

231
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:27,480
So what?

232
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,480
If their deaths can bring peace to the world

233
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,920
and secure the imperial power forever,

234
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:32,120
why not?

235
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:33,440
I see.

236
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:37,840
So it was Your Highness who gave the Empress Dowager this terrible idea.

237
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:40,240
Such a hard-thought 'good' idea.

238
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:41,730
You're so great.

239
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:42,930
I'll give you a like.

240
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,460
People's statuses may be high or low,

241
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,800
but lives are equal.

242
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,000
How can they be sacrificed at will?

243
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,600
How dare you!
